        {
            "title": "譚輝智姚焯菲張馳豪出碟力撐  4.12舉行《香港唱片店日2025》",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"譚輝智姚焯菲張馳豪出碟力撐  4.12舉行《香港唱片店日2025》。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c8aced34304d88cf073b6bca4302db97/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250314/_2025031401312620796.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">譚輝智姚焯菲張馳豪出碟力撐  4.12舉行《香港唱片店日2025》。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>香港唱片商會自1982年成立至今已有43年歷史，在剛舉行的《第十九屆（2025－2028）理事會就職典禮》上，新任會長鍾慧慧（Mimi）表示，近年多了一些新顧客購買唱片、特別是黑膠產品，要歸功於很多當時得令的中外歌手，他們不會只集中在串流市場催谷，也會照顧很想購買實體產品的樂迷，並提到去年《香港唱片店日 2024》單日銷量非常亮麗，好多樂迷一大早已在唱片店門外等候，一班歌手亦現身唱片店簽名，包括甄妮、鄭少秋、林憶蓮、盧冠廷、容祖兒、張德蘭、炎明熹、鍾柔美、姚焯菲、詹天文、張馳豪和歐信希等，外國團隊就有曾多次來香港演出的 Air Supply 和 Mr. Big 等。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"香港唱片商會《第十九屆(2025 - 2028) 理事會就職典禮。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/068ccaf8b1d5102e86afeabc94534ab0/2025-03/2025_-_2028_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        香港唱片商會《第十九屆(2025 - 2028) 理事會就職典禮。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"4月12日為香港唱片店日。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a0c4f998022deed27f4d48971c253b24/2025-03/174188530756852.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        4月12日為香港唱片店日。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>此外，她透露今年已落實參與的唱片公司包括TVB Music Group、All About Music 和風行唱片等，將會出現的歌手有吳業坤、周吉佩、古淖文、李佳、羅啟豪、譚輝智、龍婷、支嚳儀、吳大強、顏志恒、林彥言、丁文俊、黃劍文、戴祖儀、歐信希、伍富橋、姚焯菲、張馳豪、詹天文和林智樂等。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\" 當日譚輝智將出現。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ae8c281b14c7c9d3018a0c0c05c438bc/2025-03/-__17.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n         當日譚輝智將出現。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"姚焯菲\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0da9fc04a1da2af7809b6d4bc3d1620d/2025-03/-__8.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        姚焯菲\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃劍文\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3aac63ae302d565c9c6195118784c316/2025-03/-__0_1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃劍文\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"張馳豪\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/19df1ca2e20d3a9802d4a9b5dc47dad7/2025-03/-__9.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        張馳豪\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"詹天文\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/043d94fe2d1d4f084ef40434b431c6bd/2025-03/-__11.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        詹天文\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"周吉佩\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f7427c7c669c6bf874736ba308d74e28/2025-03/-__5.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        周吉佩\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\" 丁文俊\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a1e373848f34f2ee8297c139695c55c7/2025-03/-__2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"10